How to setup the server:

1. Create a mariadb database.

2. Execute the startup.sql script on the created database.

3. Configure the Class Main:
    2.1 Adjust the variable DB_URL and set it to the db url of the maria db you have created.
        Default is DB_URL = "jdbc:mariadb://localhost:3306/ticketmanagement".
    2.2 Adjust the variable DB_USER and set it to the db user of the maria db you have created
        that as all read and write rights. Default is DB_USER = "root".

4. Start the Server by running the main method of the class Main of the project Server.

5. Start the Client by running the main method of the class Main of the project Client.